    dc:creator "Shelley, Rowland M.; Hollis, Jennifer L." ;
    dc:date "2003" ;
    dc:title "A new milliped of the genus Abacion Rafinesque, 1820 from Arkansas, U. S. A. (Callipodida: Abacionidae)" ;
